Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Reagan loses Republican nomination
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjl8k
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 22 Aug 1976
Reagan loses Republican nomination at Kansas convention. Reasons behind Chinese rejection of US aid following devastating earthquake. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less